# ===========================================
# EMAIL CONFIGURATION FOR CONTACT FORM
# ===========================================
# 
# To receive contact form submissions in your Gmail inbox:
#
# STEP 1: Enable 2-Factor Authentication on your Gmail account
#         Go to: Google Account > Security > 2-Step Verification
#
# STEP 2: Generate an App Password
#         Go to: Google Account > Security > App passwords
#         Select "Mail" and your device type
#         Copy the 16-character password generated
#
# STEP 3: Set the environment variables below:
#

SMTP_EMAIL=your-gmail@gmail.com
SMTP_PASSWORD=your-16-char-app-password

# The email address where contact form messages will be sent
# (Already configured in the code as miqkniq@gmail.com)

